{{version031}}
''For Greater Healing, the divine player ability with a similar name, see [[Elyvilon]]'s page.''
{{flavour|Heals a large amount of damage to the caster's body.}}

'''Major Healing''' is a monster-only spell which restores between <code>50</code> and <code>50 + 10 * [[HD]]</code> [[hit points]]. Note that monsters can cast this spell when they are outside the player's [[line of sight]].

